rows.label: tlk70000032_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Adel and friends! I
hope you're uninjured?

rows.label: tlk70000032_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Those Gargoyle things were
pretty terrifying. If you
hadn't been there...

rows.label: tlk70000032_02_msg0003
rows.name: Well. It doesn't bear thinking about.

rows.label: tlk70000032_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I may have taken a good hit on
the old legs, but there are
others who suffered even more.

rows.label: tlk70000032_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I hope I get better soon so
I can get back to my life.
